It's fine to be alone.

18
00:02:20,190 --> 00:02:22,400
But I don't know when

19
00:02:22,710 --> 00:02:24,280
I started to relax around you.

20
00:02:32,750 --> 00:02:34,120
I'm harmless

21
00:02:35,030 --> 00:02:36,910
and honest.

22
00:02:37,310 --> 00:02:38,150
So?

23
00:02:39,000 --> 00:02:40,120
As you said,

24
