if it's right or wrong?

27
00:02:49,520 --> 00:02:50,630
Then let me make it clear first.

28
00:02:52,470 --> 00:02:53,630
I won't sacrifice myself,

29
00:02:53,750 --> 00:02:55,030
nor will I accommodate you.

30
00:02:55,520 --> 00:02:57,120
If I feel uncomfortable,

31
00:02:57,120 --> 00:02:58,590
we'll stop.

32
00:02:59,150 --> 00:02:59,990
Of course,

33
