this is a negotiation.

37
00:03:10,310 --> 00:03:11,840
Who said I was confessing to you?

38
00:03:14,870 --> 00:03:17,190
I'm giving you a chance to confess again.

39
00:03:19,360 --> 00:03:21,000
Do I have to do it again?

40
00:03:21,470 --> 00:03:23,120
- You can choose not to.
- Here it comes.

41
00:03:31,080 --> 00:03:31,920
I didn't bring any flowers.

42
00:03:33,400 --> 00:03:35,240
This will do.

43
00:03:37,840 --> 00:03:38,680
Su.

44
00:03:40,630 --> 00:03:44,750
From 15 days, 9 hours,
and 17 minutes ago to now,

45
00:03:46,150 --> 00:03:47,520
it's been four more days,

46
00:03:48,120 --> 00:03:51,430
give or take a few minutes.

47
00:03:51,430 --> 00:03:52,270
I didn't

48
