310
00:16:19,790 --> 00:16:20,630
What I meant was...

311
00:16:20,630 --> 00:16:21,960
Shut up.

312
00:16:22,390 --> 00:16:23,230
Let her talk.

313
00:16:25,360 --> 00:16:26,200
You.

314
00:16:26,200 --> 00:16:27,040
Speak.

315
00:16:27,790 --> 00:16:28,750
Didn't you just talk a lot?

316
00:16:31,150 --> 00:16:32,240
Let her apologize to me.

317
00:16:32,960 --> 00:16:34,010
What was her attitude just now?

318
00:16:39,440 --> 00:16:40,280
I apologize.

319
00:16:40,630 --> 00:16:42,840
I apologize on her behalf. I'm sorry.

320
00:16:43,080 --> 00:16:44,600
Who do you think you are?

321
00:16:45,600 --> 00:16:46,840
I want her

322
00:16:47,910 --> 00:16:49,150
to apologize.

323
00:16:50,600 --> 00:16:51,840
- Forget it, let's go.
- You shut up.

324
00:16:52,390 --> 00:16:53,710
- Watch out.
- Ma'am.

325
00:16:54,030 --> 00:16:55,200
- Are you okay?
- Get lost.

326
