329
00:17:05,270 --> 00:17:06,550
Stop hitting him, Fang!

330
00:17:06,830 --> 00:17:08,110
Fang! Fang! Stop it!

331
00:17:08,110 --> 00:17:09,590
Alright, alright, alright.

332
00:17:09,590 --> 00:17:11,270
- Stop it.
- Fang, stop it.

333
00:17:11,590 --> 00:17:12,590
