334
00:17:16,270 --> 00:17:17,110
Stop it!

335
00:17:17,270 --> 00:17:18,440
- Don't get physical.
- I'll hit you!

336
00:17:18,440 --> 00:17:19,280
Stop it.

337
00:17:19,280 --> 00:17:20,310
Stop it. Stop it.

338
00:17:20,350 --> 00:17:21,190
Go away.

339
00:17:24,270 --> 00:17:25,110
Stop it.

340
00:17:27,310 --> 00:17:28,150
Stop it.

341
00:17:29,110 --> 00:17:29,950
Fang, Fang!

342
00:17:30,110 --> 00:17:31,600
- Stop it.
- I'm telling you.

343
00:17:31,680 --> 00:17:32,960
If you continue, I'll call the police.

344
00:17:33,200 --> 00:17:34,040
Calm down.

345
00:17:34,680 --> 00:17:35,520
Calm down.

346
00:17:42,350 --> 00:17:43,310
Feeling dizzy?

347
00:17:44,350 --> 00:17:45,190
Nauseous?

348
00:17:45,480 --> 00:17:46,320
No.

349
00:17:46,720 --> 00:17:48,510
You should be especially careful tonight.

350
00:17:48,920 --> 00:17:50,240
Someone must stay by his side.

351
00:17:51,070 --> 00:17:53,920
If there's any headache,
nausea, or dizziness,

352
00:17:54,070 --> 00:17:55,230
seek medical attention promptly.

353
00:17:55,440 --> 00:17:56,280
Okay.

354
00:17:56,720 --> 00:17:58,270
Better get him a CT scan

355
00:17:58,790 --> 00:17:59,960
- to check thoroughly.
- Okay, okay.

356
00:18:16,960 --> 00:18:18,270
The wound isn't deep,

357
00:18:19,480 --> 00:18:22,440
but it's close to the eye.

358
00:18:22,830 --> 00:18:24,920
Better not to use anesthesia.

359
00:18:25,960 --> 00:18:27,000
Endure it a bit, young man.

360
00:18:28,350 --> 00:18:29,190
Alright.

361
00:18:30,200 --> 00:18:32,350
Girlfriend, hold his hand.

362
00:18:59,830 --> 00:19:00,670
It's okay.

363
00:19:00,680 --> 00:19:02,180
