374
00:19:24,350 --> 00:19:26,160
they insist you started the fight.

375
00:19:26,160 --> 00:19:27,350
From the surveillance footage,

376
00:19:27,350 --> 00:19:28,590
your punch was quite severe indeed.

377
00:19:28,880 --> 00:19:30,310
However, there was a reason for it.

378
00:19:30,440 --> 00:19:31,960
He pushed your girlfriend first, right?

379
00:19:32,510 --> 00:19:33,440
We're colleagues,

380
00:19:34,030 --> 00:19:35,000
not boyfriend and girlfriend.

381
00:19:37,920 --> 00:19:40,070
You're too young to play the hero.

382
00:19:40,750 --> 00:19:41,720
How old are you?

383
00:19:41,720 --> 00:19:42,560
Your temper is so fierce.

384
00:19:42,880 --> 00:19:43,720
Is it worth

385
00:19:43,880 --> 00:19:45,440
fighting over such a trivial matter?

386
00:19:46,000 --> 00:19:47,000
You broke so many things

387
00:19:47,110 --> 00:19:47,950
and hurt yourself.

388
00:19:48,720 --> 00:19:51,000
What if that handsome face

389
00:19:51,160 --> 00:19:52,110
gets disfigured?

390
00:19:54,440 --> 00:19:57,000
I'll pay for all the losses in the store.

391
00:19:57,440 --> 00:19:58,790
It's not just the store's loss,

392
00:19:59,070 --> 00:20:00,530
but also the other party's
medical expenses.

393
00:20:00,550 --> 00:20:02,000
At the same time, I want to remind you

394
00:20:02,550 --> 00:20:03,640
that they still have

395
00:20:03,640 --> 00:20:05,310
the right to sue you civilly.

396
00:20:05,640 --> 00:20:07,110
- You need to be clear on this.
- No, they...

397
00:20:07,110 --> 00:20:07,950
Understood.

398
00:20:08,070 --> 00:20:08,920
Officer,

399
00:20:09,960 --> 00:20:11,550
I accept any punishment.

400
00:20:12,030 --> 00:20:13,310
It's all my fault.

401
00:20:13,880 --> 00:20:15,030
Good attitude.

402
00:20:15,400 --> 00:20:17,200
That's all we need for now.

403
00:20:17,200 --> 00:20:18,800
- Is the statement finished?
- Yes.

404
00:20:19,240 --> 00:20:20,080
Review it.

405
00:20:20,110 --> 00:20:21,200
If everything's correct,

406
00:20:21,200 --> 00:20:22,040
sign it.

407
00:20:22,310 --> 00:20:24,240
Also, keep your phone on.

408
00:20:24,750 --> 00:20:26,440
We may need to contact you again.

409
00:20:26,680 --> 00:20:27,520
Okay.

410
00:20:44,920 --> 00:20:45,760
Are you okay?

411
00:20:46,480 --> 00:20:47,320
I'm fine.

412
00:21:17,400 --> 00:21:18,240
Take it slow.

413
00:21:43,400 --> 00:21:44,240
Thank you.

414
00:22:27,550 --> 00:22:28,440
Is your back okay?

415
00:22:28,720 --> 00:22:29,790
It's fine. I'm already better.

416
00:22:41,510 --> 00:22:42,440
I'll manage myself.

417
00:22:50,480 --> 00:22:51,320
I'm fine.

418
00:22:51,920 --> 00:22:52,880
It's getting late.

419
00:22:53,550 --> 00:22:54,440
You should go rest.

420
00:22:54,880 --> 00:22:57,240
The doctor said you need someone
by your side tonight.

421
00:23:02,200 --> 00:23:03,230
Where's your electric heater?

422
00:23:07,830 --> 00:23:08,960
- I don't have one.
- Really?

423
00:23:10,110 --> 00:23:10,960
It's so cold.

424
00:23:11,310 --> 00:23:12,240
How do you keep warm?

425
00:23:12,720 --> 00:23:13,560
I...

426
00:23:15,750 --> 00:23:16,590
I just shiver.

427
00:23:59,830 --> 00:24:01,160
This is the only electric heater.

428
00:24:01,750 --> 00:24:02,960
You can use it with Tiny.

429
00:24:29,920 --> 00:24:31,110
- Let me do it.
- It's okay.

430
00:24:31,110 --> 00:24:31,950
Sit there.

431
00:24:53,640 --> 00:24:54,480
Rest early.

432
00:24:59,550 --> 00:25:00,510
I'll go out first.

433
00:25:34,110 --> 00:25:34,950
I'm coming in.

434
00:25:58,790 --> 00:25:59,630
Thank you.

435
00:26:34,070 --> 00:26:34,910
Huang,

436
00:26:35,510 --> 00:26:37,240
why don't you come up and sit here?

437
00:26:37,640 --> 00:26:39,110
There's an electric blanket. It's warm.

438
00:26:43,350 --> 00:26:44,490
Please don't misunderstand me.

439
00:26:44,680 --> 00:26:45,680
I mean no harm.

440
00:26:47,070 --> 00:26:48,240
I'm just worried you might be cold.

441
00:27:39,680 --> 00:27:41,000
How do you have my photo?

442
00:27:44,590 --> 00:27:45,550
Well...

443
00:27:48,000 --> 00:27:51,880
You took me to an art exhibition once.

444
00:27:52,480 --> 00:27:53,640
I found it quite interesting.

445
00:27:54,480 --> 00:27:56,750
During the Spring Festival,
I had nothing to do,

446
00:27:57,030 --> 00:27:59,510
so I found a few free exhibitions
to visit.

447
00:28:00,550 --> 00:28:01,680
In a small gallery

448
00:28:01,750 --> 00:28:03,550
that I forgot

449
00:28:04,310 --> 00:28:05,240
its name,

450
00:28:05,480 --> 00:28:06,510
while I was browsing,

451
00:28:06,640 --> 00:28:08,790
I saw your photo on the wall,

452
00:28:09,400 --> 00:28:11,030
along with many others.

453
00:28:11,200 --> 00:28:12,040
Just like this one.

454
00:28:13,440 --> 00:28:14,280
What a coincidence.

455
00:28:14,590 --> 00:28:15,790
In an old Western-style building?

456
00:28:16,200 --> 00:28:17,640
Yes, in an old Western-style building.

457
00:28:17,640 --> 00:28:18,680
So you asked them for it?

458
00:28:20,830 --> 00:28:21,670
Actually,

459
00:28:22,680 --> 00:28:23,520
I stole it.

460
00:28:26,720 --> 00:28:29,000
I was afraid they might violate
your portrait rights.

461
00:28:31,920 --> 00:28:33,240
I intended to give it to you,

462
00:28:33,830 --> 00:28:35,440
but I haven't got the chance.

463
00:28:35,680 --> 00:28:36,640
I thought I might forget,

464
00:28:36,640 --> 00:28:37,830
so I kept it here.

465
00:28:40,480 --> 00:28:42,790
Today seems like a good day
to return it to you.

466
00:28:54,110 --> 00:28:54,950
I'll give it to you.

467
00:28:55,160 --> 00:28:56,000
I...

468
00:29:06,070 --> 00:29:07,070
Cover up a bit more.

469
00:29:07,240 --> 00:29:08,400
This room is really cold.

470
00:29:13,640 --> 00:29:14,510
Still dizzy?

471
00:29:16,680 --> 00:29:17,520
Not too much,

472
00:29:18,400 --> 00:29:19,830
just a bit lightheaded,

473
00:29:21,030 --> 00:29:23,720
like after drinking.

474
00:29:30,920 --> 00:29:31,760
Huang,

475
00:29:33,680 --> 00:29:34,520
I'm sorry.

476
00:29:35,270 --> 00:29:36,110
Today,

477
00:29:37,830 --> 00:29:39,200
you got expelled because of me.

478
00:29:41,310 --> 00:29:42,640
It's my fault.

479
00:29:46,310 --> 00:29:48,400
And that girl didn't appreciate it,

480
00:29:48,750 --> 00:29:50,270
claiming we started the fight.

481
00:29:52,440 --> 00:29:54,270
I thought that guy was tough,

482
00:29:54,350 --> 00:29:56,310
trying to intimidate us.

483
00:29:56,720 --> 00:29:58,000
Turns out he couldn't handle it.

484
00:29:58,270 --> 00:29:59,920
Didn't expect you could fight so well.

485
00:30:00,640 --> 00:30:03,000
I used to fight boys when I was little.

486
00:30:03,750 --> 00:30:05,240
They liked putting caterpillars

487
00:30:05,240 --> 00:30:06,590
in my pencil case and my schoolbag.

488
00:30:08,240 --> 00:30:09,830
No wonder you're so brave.

489
00:30:10,350 --> 00:30:11,920
You've started it since childhood.

490
00:30:12,910 --> 00:30:14,400
If we'd met back then,

491
00:30:14,400 --> 00:30:15,240
