492
00:30:15,550 --> 00:30:16,890
you wouldn't have been able to beat me.

493
00:30:16,920 --> 00:30:18,270
I couldn't bear to hit you though.

494
00:30:33,240 --> 00:30:34,920
Honestly,

495
00:30:35,480 --> 00:30:36,520
I wanted to learn martial arts

496
00:30:36,640 --> 00:30:38,270
when I was little.

497
00:30:38,790 --> 00:30:39,830
Do you want to be a hero?

498
00:30:40,590 --> 00:30:42,750
When I was a kid, I did dream of it

499
00:30:43,880 --> 00:30:47,000
to act on injustice.

500
00:30:51,510 --> 00:30:53,680
But as I grew up, I got more cowardly.

501
00:30:53,830 --> 00:30:56,160
I ended up just running away

502
00:30:56,920 --> 00:30:57,960
from injustice.

503
00:31:11,200 --> 00:31:12,040
Anyway,

504
00:31:12,510 --> 00:31:13,550
thank you

505
00:31:15,830 --> 00:31:18,480
for giving me a chance
to be a hero today.

506
00:31:29,830 --> 00:31:31,030
Why is your hand so cold?

507
00:32:01,550 --> 00:32:02,390
Tiny.

508
00:32:03,510 --> 00:32:04,590
Why are you here?

509
00:32:06,720 --> 00:32:07,560
Hey.

510
00:32:12,640 --> 00:32:13,720
Why aren't you sleeping?

511
00:32:16,440 --> 00:32:17,310
Little one.

512
00:32:25,030 --> 00:32:25,870
Tiny.

513
00:32:26,160 --> 00:32:27,000
Tiny.

514
00:32:27,830 --> 00:32:28,670
Tiny.

515
00:32:29,690 --> 00:32:33,640
♪A rose alive♪

516
00:32:35,590 --> 00:32:36,430
Tiny.

517
00:32:38,400 --> 00:32:39,240
Tiny.

518
00:32:42,880 --> 00:32:43,720
Tiny.

519
00:32:44,240 --> 00:32:45,080
There, there, there.

520
00:32:46,440 --> 00:32:47,280
Tiny.

521
00:32:47,480 --> 00:32:48,760
Come here.

522
00:32:48,760 --> 00:32:52,380
♪Like a splash of red in a dull world♪

523
00:32:52,510 --> 00:32:54,070
How does it know

524
00:32:54,240 --> 00:32:55,510
