527
00:32:59,920 --> 00:33:00,760
Come on.

528
00:33:01,510 --> 00:33:02,350
Let's go.

529
00:33:02,450 --> 00:33:05,370
♪The warmest corner of my heart♪

530
00:33:06,060 --> 00:33:08,720
♪Give my love to her♪

531
00:33:09,110 --> 00:33:11,950
♪Give everything to her♪

532
00:33:12,210 --> 00:33:16,970
♪Watch her bloom proudly, just for me♪

533
00:33:17,390 --> 00:33:19,640
