(Chatting with Endless Life)
Happy birthday, Sister-in-law.

567
00:35:18,190 --> 00:35:19,320
Who's your sister-in-law?

568
00:35:20,440 --> 00:35:22,000
I really didn't expect

569
00:35:22,190 --> 00:35:23,150
someone like you

570
00:35:23,150 --> 00:35:25,550
would date a blockhead like my brother.

571
00:35:25,920 --> 00:35:26,840
What am I like?

572
00:35:28,230 --> 00:35:29,550
It's you.

573
00:35:31,000 --> 00:35:32,150
Anyway, I can't imagine

574
00:35:32,150 --> 00:35:33,440
what you'd be like in a relationship.

575
00:35:35,230 --> 00:35:38,190
By the way, I'll give you the gift
next time I go back.

576
00:35:39,230 --> 00:35:40,190
What did my brother give you?

577
00:35:42,840 --> 00:35:43,680
Guess.

578
00:35:44,190 --> 00:35:45,840
Lipstick, or maybe perfume?

579
00:36:01,150 --> 00:36:02,320
That big fool.

580
00:36:03,190 --> 00:36:04,030
Oh, my.

581
00:36:06,400 --> 00:36:09,480
He insisted that we met over dumbbells,

582
00:36:09,480 --> 00:36:10,870
so he absolutely had to give me dumbbells

583
00:36:10,970 --> 00:36:12,150
to commemorate it.

584
00:36:12,150 --> 00:36:13,360
It's truly unbelievable.

585
00:36:16,880 --> 00:36:18,840
Then you should hit his foot again.

586
00:36:18,840 --> 00:36:20,280
That would be even more memorable.

587
00:36:32,190 --> 00:36:34,190
How are things between you and that guy?

588
00:36:40,000 --> 00:36:40,880
You're blushing.

589
00:36:45,190 --> 00:36:46,510
Shanghai's too hot.

590
00:36:50,960 --> 00:36:51,800
You like him?

591
00:36:56,590 --> 00:36:58,230
I think you two are quite alike.

592
00:36:59,320 --> 00:37:01,070
You don't like me, do you?

593
00:37:11,360 --> 00:37:12,360
I mean

594
00:37:17,190 --> 00:37:18,960
you're both really smart

595
00:37:19,320 --> 00:37:20,190
and work really hard.

596
00:37:21,320 --> 00:37:22,630
You seem cold,

597
00:37:22,760 --> 00:37:24,670
but you're actually kind-hearted.

598
00:37:26,880 --> 00:37:27,720
Rose,

599
00:37:28,840 --> 00:37:29,880
I envy you so much.

600
00:37:31,800 --> 00:37:34,440
It's always about weighing pros and cons
for most people.

601
00:37:34,960 --> 00:37:35,800
But you're different.

602
00:37:36,510 --> 00:37:38,710
You seem to be born
with the ability to love.

603
00:37:39,230 --> 00:37:40,840
What a rare gift.

604
00:37:51,320 --> 00:37:52,550
Su, do you love my brother?

605
00:37:57,110 --> 00:37:59,000
I don't have that much talent for love,

606
00:38:00,760 --> 00:38:02,110
but I'm trying to learn.

607
00:38:16,480 --> 00:38:17,550
Oh, my.

608
00:38:19,190 --> 00:38:20,920
This call couldn't have come
at a better time.

609
00:38:29,110 --> 00:38:30,190
What did you find out?

610
00:38:31,320 --> 00:38:32,280
Yanji?

611
00:38:33,150 --> 00:38:34,810
Why didn't he go
to Harbin Institute of Technology?

612
00:38:36,590 --> 00:38:37,960
He did his undergrad at Fudan,

613
00:38:39,070 --> 00:38:40,110
and he even got a scholarship.

614
00:38:40,590 --> 00:38:41,430
Anything else?

615
00:38:42,760 --> 00:38:43,960
Is it true or not?

616
00:38:44,550 --> 00:38:45,390
Anything else?

617
00:38:47,670 --> 00:38:48,510
Alright.

618
00:38:49,110 --> 00:38:49,950
I got it.

619
00:38:50,630 --> 00:38:51,470
Thanks.

620
00:38:54,960 --> 00:38:56,710
Though he seems fine,

621
00:38:56,710 --> 00:38:57,590
from what I heard,

622
00:38:58,110 --> 00:39:01,030
he's just an ordinary and practical guy.

623
00:39:01,190 --> 00:39:03,030
He's leagues away
from being right for my sister.

624
00:39:03,710 --> 00:39:05,300
He's not even her boyfriend yet,

625
00:39:05,310 --> 00:39:06,820
and you're already
checking his background.

626
00:39:06,830 --> 00:39:07,880
That's why

627
00:39:07,880 --> 00:39:09,920
I need to check it now.

628
00:39:13,230 --> 00:39:15,320
Do you think one's background matters?

629
00:39:17,280 --> 00:39:18,120
It depends on the person.

630
00:39:18,360 --> 00:39:20,000
If they're good,
the background won't matter.

631
00:39:21,510 --> 00:39:22,670
Then why are you investigating

632
00:39:22,670 --> 00:39:24,110
Rose's boyfriend?

633
00:39:24,710 --> 00:39:26,360
If he's not good, how can she like him?

634
00:39:26,590 --> 00:39:27,840
Don't you know Rose?

635
00:39:27,840 --> 00:39:29,480
Once she falls in love,
she disregards everything.

636
00:39:35,030 --> 00:39:36,110
You're right.

637
00:39:36,510 --> 00:39:37,480
She's an adult now.

638
00:39:37,480 --> 00:39:39,550
I shouldn't interfere so much.

639
00:39:46,510 --> 00:39:49,360
Though Rose might not always
make the right choices...

640
00:39:49,630 --> 00:39:51,230
Wait. The weight is wrong.

641
00:39:52,070 --> 00:39:54,000
I thought it was heavy.

642
00:39:56,230 --> 00:39:57,880
But she has a high margin of error.

643
00:39:59,030 --> 00:40:00,280
What's that margin of error?

644
00:40:01,230 --> 00:40:02,110
Drop your shoulders.

645
00:40:03,480 --> 00:40:04,320
I've noticed

646
00:40:04,320 --> 00:40:06,110
everyone in your family
seems to have this ability.

647
00:40:06,880 --> 00:40:08,510
Even if you make the wrong choice,

648
00:40:08,800 --> 00:40:10,760
you can still self-correct and improve.

649
00:40:11,360 --> 00:40:13,360
Are you praising her or me?

650
00:40:14,920 --> 00:40:16,000
Can't you tell?

651
00:40:16,190 --> 00:40:17,630
I'm just giving you a heads-up.

652
00:40:18,360 --> 00:40:20,590
If one day we can't part amicably,

653
00:40:20,590 --> 00:40:21,550
remember

654
00:40:22,320 --> 00:40:23,440
to get back on track.

655
00:40:23,550 --> 00:40:24,390
Don't blame me,

656
00:40:24,590 --> 00:40:25,710
and don't bother me.

657
00:40:25,880 --> 00:40:27,280
That's not gonna happen.

658
00:40:29,150 --> 00:40:31,840
I'm sure you're the one for me.

659
00:40:33,670 --> 00:40:35,320
You can't get rid of me now.

660
00:40:35,630 --> 00:40:36,630
I can't take it anymore.

661
00:40:37,840 --> 00:40:39,480
No, no. Give me three more.

662
00:40:39,800 --> 00:40:41,000
I'll help you. Come on.

663
00:40:41,440 --> 00:40:42,280
Three.

664
00:40:43,400 --> 00:40:44,240
You can do it.

665
00:40:48,400 --> 00:40:49,240
Ms. Jiang.

666
00:40:51,920 --> 00:40:52,760
Alright, alright.

667
00:40:52,920 --> 00:40:54,510
When did you become so needy?

668
00:40:56,070 --> 00:40:57,280
You're the first person to come

669
00:40:57,280 --> 00:40:58,670
to Shanghai to see me,
except for my family.

670
00:40:58,920 --> 00:41:00,110
Don't flatter yourself.

671
00:41:00,400 --> 00:41:01,440
I came for a business trip,

672
00:41:01,550 --> 00:41:02,760
not just to see you.

673
00:41:02,880 --> 00:41:04,630
I don't care. I'm happy.

674
00:41:06,840 --> 00:41:07,960
You're not mad at me, are you?

675
00:41:08,280 --> 00:41:09,800
When did I get mad at you?

676
00:41:10,110 --> 00:41:11,320
You didn't reply to my text messages.

677
00:41:11,630 --> 00:41:13,440
I'm your boss, not your friend.

678
00:41:13,470 --> 00:41:15,320
If you wish me a happy new year,
do I have to return the favor?

679
00:41:16,320 --> 00:41:17,480
You can give me some New Year's money.

680
00:41:18,440 --> 00:41:19,280
Sit.

681
00:41:19,800 --> 00:41:21,290
I'm here to test
how well you've been studying.

682
00:41:21,510 --> 00:41:23,480
What am I thinking right now?

683
00:41:23,960 --> 00:41:26,320
Ms. Jiang, I'm not a fortune-teller.

684
00:41:27,110 --> 00:41:27,960
Okay, okay.

685
00:41:28,280 --> 00:41:30,110
I'm not interested
in what you've learned.

686
00:41:31,840 --> 00:41:33,320
Why did you come dressed like this?

687
00:41:33,510 --> 00:41:34,350
Also,

688
00:41:34,760 --> 00:41:36,070
why aren't you wearing lipstick?

689
00:41:36,320 --> 00:41:39,280
Huang Yimei,
how did you become so sloppy?

690
00:41:39,760 --> 00:41:41,200
Do you still remember
how to do your makeup?

691
00:41:41,230 --> 00:41:42,920
There's a charity event today.

692
00:41:43,230 --> 00:41:44,070
You'll accompany me.

693
00:41:44,230 --> 00:41:45,070
I haven't attended

694
00:41:45,080 --> 00:41:46,590
such an event in a long time.

695
00:41:46,920 --> 00:41:48,440
You can't lose your social skills.

696
00:41:48,760 --> 00:41:50,590
Use this opportunity to review it.

697
00:41:51,000 --> 00:41:53,010
Go home and change into a formal dress
before you come find me.

698
00:41:54,280 --> 00:41:55,320
I don't have a dress.

699
00:41:55,480 --> 00:41:56,440
This is Shanghai.

700
00:41:56,710 --> 00:41:58,400
Don't you have a decent dress?

701
00:41:58,710 --> 00:42:00,550
Don't tell anyone
that you've worked for me.

702
00:42:01,360 --> 00:42:02,360
There are three hours left.

703
00:42:02,360 --> 00:42:03,840
You'd better go buy one.
Don't claim you're poor.

704
00:42:04,110 --> 00:42:05,670
You used to be
so willing to spend on yourself.

705
00:42:05,670 --> 00:42:06,670
I know that.

706
00:42:06,960 --> 00:42:07,800
See you later. Bye-bye.

707
00:42:37,150 --> 00:42:37,990
Wait a minute.

708
00:42:51,840 --> 00:42:53,630
I just wanted to ask you

709
00:42:54,030 --> 00:42:55,400
if you wanted to have dinner together.

710
00:42:55,920 --> 00:42:56,760
Sorry.

711
00:42:56,760 --> 00:42:57,600
I can't tonight.

712
00:42:59,800 --> 00:43:00,640
That's okay.

713
00:43:01,000 --> 00:43:01,840
What do you need?

714
00:43:10,200 --> 00:43:12,230
♪Rain♪

715
00:43:13,170 --> 00:43:15,900
♪Falls on my forehead♪

716
00:43:17,130 --> 00:43:21,170
♪The wind fills my sleeves♪

717
00:43:21,170 --> 00:43:24,880
♪I pass through intersections♪

718
00:43:25,200 --> 00:43:27,570
♪Changing trains♪

719
00:43:29,170 --> 00:43:31,820
♪Stopping at each station♪

720
00:43:33,190 --> 00:43:37,180
♪Encounters in the bustling streets♪

721
00:43:37,180 --> 00:43:41,040
♪Freedom in farewells♪

722
00:43:41,510 --> 00:43:43,470
♪May I accompany myself♪

723
00:43:44,460 --> 00:43:48,280
♪Throughout this life's journey♪

724
00:43:48,490 --> 00:43:52,840
♪Loving someone is the best♪

725
00:43:53,400 --> 00:43:57,030
♪But not obligatory♪

726
00:43:57,280 --> 00:43:59,980
♪As long as the wind blows♪

727
00:44:00,420 --> 00:44:04,000
♪Good luck is on the way♪

728
00:44:04,370 --> 00:44:08,640
♪Happiness should come from within♪

729
00:44:09,130 --> 00:44:12,710
♪No need for anyone else♪

730
00:44:13,120 --> 00:44:16,720
♪Watching the sunset along the way♪

731
00:44:17,030 --> 00:44:20,880
♪Like flowers sent from afar♪

732
00:44:21,090 --> 00:44:23,240
♪Rainy or sunny, keep moving forward♪

733
00:44:23,240 --> 00:44:25,420
♪I want to move forward♪

734
00:44:25,420 --> 00:44:29,110
♪So let go of my hand♪

735
00:44:29,110 --> 00:44:32,780
♪The road can be run on♪

736
00:44:33,130 --> 00:44:36,910
♪It can also be danced on♪

737
00:44:37,160 --> 00:44:39,510
♪The crossroads I want to go to♪

738
00:44:39,510 --> 00:44:41,550
♪Are beyond where you stand♪

739
00:44:41,550 --> 00:44:48,180
♪No regrets left behind♪

740
00:44:49,160 --> 00:44:52,740
♪May I keep moving forward♪

741
00:44:53,130 --> 00:44:55,580
♪Whether rainy or sunny♪

742
00:44:55,580 --> 00:44:57,470
♪Empty-handed along the way♪

743
00:44:57,470 --> 00:45:01,210
♪Only needing health♪

744
00:45:01,210 --> 00:45:03,650
♪Happiness♪

745
00:45:05,060 --> 00:45:08,030
♪and a free spirit♪

746
00:45:09,110 --> 00:45:10,230
♪Like a bird in flight♪

747
00:45:10,230 --> 00:45:12,910
♪Born♪

748
00:45:13,190 --> 00:45:17,590
♪With the entire♪

749
00:45:18,500 --> 00:45:23,620
♪Sky♪
